{"tid":2458403,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李小加爆兒子曾炒GME：每個年青人一生中都應該參與一次革命","createTime":"2021-03-23T11:36:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T13:24:21.000Z","uid":41343,"like":31,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"bbfaa9d8e1b7de4d51aa5f2a60aa9b05ade898a8","tid":2458403,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T11:36:00.000Z","msg":"港交所（388）前行政總裁李小加出席論壇時談到，其剛大學畢業的兒子曾參與遊戲驛站（美：GME）「挾淡倉」一役；他表示未有着兒子不要買入，還稱：「每個年青人一生中都應該參與一次革命，這是你的一個革命。」<br />\n<br />\n李小加出席第24屆瑞信亞洲投資論壇，談到港府上調股票印花稅一事。他表示，在擔任港交所行政總裁時一直與業界合作尋找方法，期望可降低股票印花稅，故對港府決意上調稅率的消息感驚訝。<br />\n<br />\n他認為，上調有關稅率對量化交易（Quantitative Trading）的影響最大，但強調印花稅上調不會令港股市場變得不再吸引。他表示，希望當局在交投維持高位及經濟復蘇時，能檢討印花稅率，「但下調稅率經常是難於上調稅率。」<br />\n<br />\n早前，港交所公開表示正研究引入「特殊目的收購公司」（SPAC）機制的可行性；但李小加認為，即使香港引入SPAC機制，亦不能藉此繞過現時的上市要求，料在SPAC完成併購交易時，仍須要經過現行的上市程序。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210323/5NTMK2W7E5CHDAENOZP6ED4RUM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210323%2F5NTMK2W7E5CHDAENOZP6ED4RUM%2F&d=9ZLePgUN12BIej1hBtk97YeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=aaee4829\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210323%2F5NTMK2W7E5CHDAENOZP6ED4RUM%2F&h=2d09a693\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210323/5NTMK2W7E5CHDAENOZP6ED4RUM/</a>"},{"pid":"cde59405cc99b16fccaefeb7e5ae7d8a07b06d5c","tid":2458403,"uid":2054,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T11:37:24.000Z","msg":"時代(Stop)革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abf93bfa51c13a1140e5cc81bd5f067670c10f9b","tid":2458403,"uid":38904,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T11:38:26.000Z","msg":"身體係革命嘅本錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi